@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

title package-manager 远端 MCP 部署视图（自动探测在线/离线路由）

node "Local PC" {
  [opencode\nmodel: glm-5] as OpenCode
  [Skill\npackage-manager-online-offline-auto-install] as Skill
  [Local stage script\npm_offline_stage_and_upload.py] as Stage
}

cloud "Network" {
  [HTTP(S) /mcp] as Net
  [Artifact Source\nOBS repo] as Repo
}

node "Remote Host / Container" {
  [package_manager.mcp_server\n(FastMCP streamable-http)] as MCP
  [Auth Layer\nStatic Token / HMAC Token\nScope: pm:read, pm:write, pm:admin] as Auth
  [control_plane.py\nwhitelist tools] as CP
  [install lock\n.mcp_install.lock] as Lock
  [package-manager binary] as Bin
  database "install_state\n.package-manager/.install_state.yaml" as State
  database "config/packages.yaml" as Cfg
  folder "offline artifacts\n_internal/packages" as OfflinePkg
}

OpenCode --> Skill : 自然语言安装请求
Skill --> OpenCode : 生成工具调用计划
OpenCode --> Net : call pm_probe_network
Net --> MCP
MCP --> Auth : verify token + scopes
Auth --> CP : allow/reject
CP --> Cfg : read runtime config
CP --> MCP : recommended_mode
MCP --> OpenCode

OpenCode --> Net : online 分支: pm_skill_install_guarded
Net --> MCP
CP --> Lock : acquire/release
CP --> Bin : run --name/--dry-run
Bin --> Repo : download (if needed)
Bin --> State : update install state
CP --> MCP : structured result
MCP --> OpenCode

OpenCode --> Stage : offline 分支: local download/upload
Stage --> Repo : download package + .p7s
Stage --> OfflinePkg : upload artifacts
OpenCode --> Net : pm_check_offline_artifacts + pm_skill_install_guarded + pm_status
Net --> MCP
MCP --> OpenCode : final status

@enduml
